   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.03" end="00:00:04.46" region="speaker">Adding products to your business profile is a</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.46" end="00:00:07.46" region="speaker">natural part of growth and progress.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.46" end="00:00:10.43" region="speaker">As this modification could potentially impact your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.43" end="00:00:12.93" region="speaker">projections of how much business you plan to do</p>
         <p begin="00:00:12.93" end="00:00:15.40" region="speaker">with the government, you will need to review and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:15.40" end="00:00:17.86" region="speaker">update your Commercial Sales Practice by clicking</p>
         <p begin="00:00:17.86" end="00:00:19.56" region="speaker">&quot;Revise.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:19.56" end="00:00:22.20" region="speaker">Updating your CSP is covered in a different</p>
         <p begin="00:00:22.20" end="00:00:23.20" region="speaker">video.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:23.20" end="00:00:26.40" region="speaker">To &quot;Add a Product&quot; to your schedule contract, you</p>
         <p begin="00:00:26.40" end="00:00:28.70" region="speaker">need to provide a detailed description of the product</p>
         <p begin="00:00:28.70" end="00:00:30.36" region="speaker">to be added.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:30.36" end="00:00:33.93" region="speaker">A goal here is to make the review of the CO as easy</p>
         <p begin="00:00:33.93" end="00:00:35.30" region="speaker">as possible.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:35.30" end="00:00:38.00" region="speaker">Some information you can provide may include: the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:38.00" end="00:00:41.06" region="speaker">SINs against which the product is applicable, a</p>
         <p begin="00:00:41.06" end="00:00:44.00" region="speaker">detailed description of the item, its packaging,</p>
         <p begin="00:00:44.00" end="00:00:46.86" region="speaker">contents, and dimensions where relevant, any</p>
         <p begin="00:00:46.86" end="00:00:49.83" region="speaker">warranties or service coverage&apos;s offered, and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:49.83" end="00:00:52.66" region="speaker">Any other information you think may be important for</p>
         <p begin="00:00:52.66" end="00:00:55.66" region="speaker">the CO in reviewing your mod request.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:55.66" end="00:00:57.30" region="speaker">When you are finished entering a detailed</p>
         <p begin="00:00:57.30" end="00:00:60.76" region="speaker">description, click &quot;save&quot; and continue.</p>
